articles.description: Bonnies big man LaDarien Griffin slams home the go-ahead bucket and Rhode Island's Jared Terrell's three is no good as the St. Bonaventure student section storms the court.
articles.headline: St. Bonaventure knocks off No. 16 Rhode Island in dramatic fashion

articles.description: James Towns scored 20 points, Kahlil Dukes added 17 and the pair fueled a second-half rally after Niagara lost high-scoring guard Matt Scott to edge Iona 85-84 on Friday night in a meeting of the third- and fourth-place teams in the Metro Atlantic...
articles.headline: Niagara overcomes loss of Scott in 85-84 win over Iona

articles.description: No. 21 Texas A&M responded to its return to the Top 25 by losing at Missouri on Wednesday and now the Aggies likely must win at Arkansas on Saturday to remain in the rankings.
articles.headline: No. 21 Texas A&M faces tough test at Arkansas

articles.description: Kameron Chatman had his ninth double-double of the season with 26 points and 11 rebounds to help Detroit Mercy beat Youngstown State 94-84 on Friday night.
articles.headline: Detroit Mercy outlasts Youngstown State 94-84

articles.description: Louisville hosts No. 14 North Carolina on Saturday night in what is likely the Cardinals' biggest home game of the season.
articles.headline: Louisville seeks signature win vs. No. 14 UNC

videos.description: Tra Holder brings the ball up the court and splashes home a 3-pointer for the Sun Devils in the first half.
videos.headline: Arizona State's Holder on target from deep

videos.description: Justin Bibbins hits his defender with a fake pass and drills the shot from beyond the arc for the Utes.
videos.headline: Utah's Bibbins drains 3-pointer

videos.description: Shannon Evans II puts the moves on his defender and knocks down a 3-pointer for the Sun Devils in the second half.
videos.headline: Arizona State's Evans hits sick crossover, drills 3-pointer

videos.description: Remmy Martin gets the ASU faithful on their feet with a deep 3-pointer in the second half.
videos.headline: Arizona State's Martin sinks big 3-pointer

videos.description: Remmy Martin capitalizes on a Utah turnover and takes it all the way to the rack for the lead in the second half.
videos.headline: Arizona State's Martin gives Sun Devils the lead

videos.description: ASU's Curtain of Distraction opens to reveal a large man with an even larger wrecking ball.
videos.headline: Arizona State's Curtain of Distraction is hilarious

videos.description: Tra Holder ends an exciting sequence of shot attempts, blocks, and loose balls with a mid-range jumper for the Sun Devils.
videos.headline: Arizona State's Holder sinks jumper on wild play
